  <brief_title>Effects of an Amino Acid Mixture on Gastrointestinal Function, Inflammation and Fluid Balance: A Pilot Study in Patients With Inflammatory Bowel Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of an Amino Acid Mixture Versus a Sugar Based Sports Drink on Gastrointestinal Function, Inflammation and Fluid Balance: A Pilot Study in Patients With Inflammatory Bowel Disease</official_title>
